column5: Hi. what happened to the thread on the toll both?
It's still here but nobody has posted anything new ... so it's been bumped to the next page.
I just bumped it back to the first page..

The report I heard was that they do have a toll booth and some people are stopping and others aren't. The OPP is sitting close by but aren't doing anything unless there is a problem like a crash of some sorts.
